                  "value": "<h2><a data-udi=\"umb://document/2034af5890894c269599623d112de8bd\" href=\"/{localLink:umb://document/2034af5890894c269599623d112de8bd}\" title=\"Fra tro til viden\">Fra tro til viden</a></h2>\n<p>The purpose of<span> </span><em>The Third Testament</em><span> </span>is to raise the great questions about life out of the hazy area of belief into personal experience and well founded knowledge. The basic premise of the work is that the mystery of life can be explained scientifically.</p>\n<h2><a data-udi=\"umb://document/8b1923debc314d9581fbcd3fd93c8a1a\" href=\"/{localLink:umb://document/8b1923debc314d9581fbcd3fd93c8a1a}\" title=\"Artikler\">Artikler and Brochurer</a></h2>\n<p>Read articles and selected texts by Martinus and download brochurer.</p>",
